high_descs: Turn left, walk down the hallway, turn left into the bedroom at the end of the hallway, and stop in front of the bed.
Close the laptop on the bed and pick up the laptop.
Turn around and face the small wooden desk.
Place the laptop on top of the desk.
Turn right, walk out of the bedroom, turn right down the hallway, turn right into the living room, and then stand in front of the sofa.
Close the laptop on top of the couch and pick up the laptop.
Turn around, turn to the right, turn left down the hallway, turn left into the bedroom at the end of the hallway, and stand in front of the small wooden desk.
Put the laptop down on top of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Collect the laptops placing them on top of the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bed.
Take the laptop from the bed.
Turn around and go near the desk.
Put the laptop on the desk.
Turn around and go to the sofa in the living room.
Take another laptop from the couch.
Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Put the laptop on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Collect the laptop and placed on the desk.

high_descs: Turn left go down the hall to the last door on the left, go straight across toward the bed.
Pick up the laptop from the bed.
Turn around to the desk.
Place the laptop in the left back corner of the desk.
Turn right at the door, go toward the TV, go across to the sofa.
Pick up the laptop on the sofa.
Head back to the desk.
Place the laptop on the desk in front of the other laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place two laptops on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the bed .
Pick up laptop from the bed.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right.
Place laptop on the desk.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the sofa.
Pick up laptop from the bed.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right.
Place laptop on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Collecting laptop from different places and arranging them on a desk.
